text: Novyye Chebenki () is a rural locality (a selo) in Novochebenkinsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 593 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Isyangulovo, 4 km from Ishemgul. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Novyye Chebenki
